scriptComments: Sets the tempoYou can use this at the start of any bar to change the tempo
Adds a noteParemeters:- Start time (beats from the start of the bar)- Notes (the note to play)- Duration (in bars)- Voice (instrument to play the note with)- Volume (how loud the note is)
